== 花絮 ==
该剧耗资巨大，仅仅是“雪山对决”就耗资4000万人民币。<ref name="fish" >{{cite web |url=http://ent.sina.com.cn/v/m/2013-11-18/15574044859.shtml |title=《雪山飞狐》韩国开播 聂远掀经典武侠热 |accessdate=2013 |publisher=新浪网 |work= |language=zh-hans |archive-date=2020-07-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200717230717/http://ent.sina.com.cn/v/m/2013-11-18/15574044859.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>

2013年11月，该剧登陆[[韩国|韩国]][[中华TV|中华TV]]。<ref name="fish" />韩国《[[朝鲜日报|朝鲜日报]]》称：“中国电视剧凭借服装华丽、弘大精良的制作场景日益受到韩国观众热捧”是这部电视剧在韩国播放的重要原因。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://news.xinhuanet.com/ent/2013-11/18/c_125717708.htm|title=《雪山飞狐》今晚韩国开播 聂远再掀经典武侠热|accessdate=2013|publisher=新华网|work=|language=zh-hans|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140408213031/http://news.xinhuanet.com/ent/2013-11/18/c_125717708.htm|archivedate=2014-04-08}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://ent.ynet.com/3.1/1311/18/8454022.html|title=《雪山飞狐》今晚韩国开播 聂远掀经典武侠热|accessdate=2013|publisher=北青网|work=|language=zh-hans|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304205825/http://ent.ynet.com/3.1/1311/18/8454022.html|archivedate=2016-03-04}}</ref>

聂远夸赞导演王晶是“鬼才”。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://ent.sina.com.cn/v/m/2008-01-07/16451865368.shtml |title=《雪山飞狐》聂远谈王晶不愧是个“鬼才”导演 |accessdate=2008 |publisher=新浪网 |work= |language=zh-hans |archive-date=2020-07-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200717230727/http://ent.sina.com.cn/v/m/2008-01-07/16451865368.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>

该剧在中国大陆播出之后，收视率颇高，但是观众质疑该剧“太时尚”，胡斐的“辫子”都没有了。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://ent.sina.com.cn/v/m/2008-01-29/12071896213.shtml |title=聂远回应新版《雪山飞狐》争议 只想完成武侠梦 |accessdate=2008 |publisher=新浪网 |work= |language=zh-hans |archive-date=2020-07-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200717230732/http://ent.sina.com.cn/v/m/2008-01-29/12071896213.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://ent.sina.com.cn/v/m/2008-01-24/15561890877.shtml |title=《雪山飞狐》被批太时尚 聂远回应这不是历史剧 |accessdate=2008 |publisher=新浪网 |work= |language=zh-hans |archive-date=2020-07-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200717230804/http://ent.sina.com.cn/v/m/2008-01-24/15561890877.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>

